Bootstrap equations: a simple example 
 

Let us consider the simple example to illuminate the general scheme
discussed in the previous sections. It will allow us to show
explicitly how to obtain the bootstrap equations for the parameters of
a rational function of two variables, restricted by the corresponding
analyticity conditions.  This example obtains an explicit solution and
makes the terminology more transparent.

Consider the rational function of two complex variables
